title: Egg-free carrot cake
ingredients: ['170g caster sugar', '60g soft brown sugar', '280g plain flour', '1 1/2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '115g butter, melted', '100ml soya milk', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '230g finely grated carrots', '180g chopped walnuts (or sultanas)']
